{"tid":1404196,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"做物資站有感，大家請入","createTime":"2019-08-04T03:17:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T06:31:21.000Z","uid":14185,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8315439a0d94e91664814761b8acfc9b7898c4ec","tid":1404196,"uid":14185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:17:57.000Z","msg":"琴日發夢既時候幫手做物資站<br />\n首先 多謝廣大市民願意出錢出力<br />\n但有幾樣野想提醒番大家<br />\n想令有心人既錢真係用得其所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1）唔好買n95口罩<br />\n因為佢對前線防催淚彈係完全無作用，<br />\n平時用黎遮樣，長期帶住又好焗。<br />\n所以無乜人會拎，但同時又好多人買黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多人想要韓式款黑色口罩，防花粉個隻，<br />\n可能戴上面無咁焗，比較受歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2）生理鹽水normal saline<br />\n好多人會prefer 一排排細支裝（10ml），<br />\n或者有個吱頭，好似con水個種，方便洗眼。<br />\n當然大支1000ml個款沖身較方便，<br />\n但壞處係，開左樽，即係用過既我地都唔敢再用，<br />\n好容易浪費左大半支。<br />\n急救組亦都提醒大家唔好買玻璃樽個隻。<br />\n<br />\n3）chlorhexidine ，即係粉紅洗傷口水，<br />\n有物資過盛既情況出現。<br />\n同樣prefer一小包個隻，方便帶係身。<br />\n其實仲有好多急救用品剩底左，<br />\n包括好多敷料，我地已經瘋狂叫啲fa team過黎，<br />\n拎走有用既野，但無奈佢地都帶唔到咁多野上路。<br />\n<br />\n如果大家有心買急救用品，<br />\n都可以自己帶定啲係身，做流動物資站，<br />\n有傷患時，即時俾到現場first aid team黎用。<br />\n堆曬係物資站，會浪費左嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個係重點！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4）<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">現金卷唔好再俾物資站</span>！！<br />\n<br />\n做過物資站都知呢個崗位都幾忙。<br />\n要幫手整理啲物資，派俾有需要既手足，<br />\n撤個時又要諗點散貨等，一秒都無時間睇手機。<br />\n<br />\n琴日執野時，發現有熱心市民，<br />\n放左幾張各價值500既迪x儂現金券係堆口罩到，<br />\n嘩屌，嚇撚死，差啲浪費左手足既心血。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有大量惠康百佳、m記餐券。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好偷偷地放底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地都好驚去keep關於錢銀既野，<br />\n一來情況混亂，驚跌左幾張。<br />\n二來我地唔知點俾到有需要既手足，<br />\n因為大家黎攞一定係攞裝備、口罩手套個啲，<br />\n唔會有人開口話要錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 夾硬塞又無謂。<br />\n<br />\n希望買左現金券既人，<br />\n會願意走上前線，觀察下邊啲人係有需要，<br />\n俾啲年輕啲無咩經濟能力既手足啦！！<br />\n<br />\n5) 請大家想捐既就捐裝備！<br />\n頭罩、高階口罩濾嘴、護膝、行山仗、<br />\n手套（防割款最多人要、防火既for滅火隊、普通勞工手套都要）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而保鮮紙，希望大家除左放底之外，<br />\n不如試下走上較前線既位置，<br />\n落手買埋啲手足包手腳。<br />\n我地無咁多人手去處理咁大量既保鮮紙啊，<br />\n次次都要散貨，都比較浪費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後多謝大家既付出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日將軍澳/港島西再戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0ab38362cc7d6adc67ebe465e63091b5d2e1a39","tid":1404196,"uid":14185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:20:05.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c5fb5c76c24eb990e78799e69d9a8b4edc5d878","tid":1404196,"uid":14185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:20:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a4aff631758ee1dfc4ed8836f49da4ab0044a71","tid":1404196,"uid":14185,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:24:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ace635794736cef3330df23237e15e6bf32f732e","tid":1404196,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:25:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆 不分化<br />\n明白大家唔同意見<br />\n呢篇野原意唔係反港獨<br />\n而係希望大家集中翻五大訴求</span></span><br />\n港獨？小心啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1400357\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1400357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2737eb7261f5651ec22b693322bbbb88929891e3","tid":1404196,"uid":261169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:25:36.000Z","msg":"有物資最好自己袋住行"},{"pid":"c3c73f08dd9b6511d4318cb3c5fb932d5616e008","tid":1404196,"uid":221192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:27:31.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d72405c80d12a857022fd10003964919e2e87215","tid":1404196,"uid":14185,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2737eb7261f5651ec22b693322bbbb88929891e3","tid":1404196,"uid":261169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:25:36.000Z","msg":"有物資最好自己袋住行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:28:02.000Z","msg":"岩呀，好多人扔曬啲野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n負荷好大，本身想散貨，<br />\n點知愈堆愈多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea8f81433a4ec1655f490cdcfbb9c6c4475d3304","tid":1404196,"uid":149833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:51:57.000Z","msg":"對物資方面認知多咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n知點做了"},{"pid":"c464f377dd1e3f398ac3ac6516904cd74946cc95","tid":1404196,"uid":293486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:04:53.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"3d509ae6d3b38e6d7af71bc8b3a13368b4fd73d2","tid":1404196,"uid":278650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:31:21.000Z","msg":"推"}]}